sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { InfoSec, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, InfoColumn, TextWrapper, TopLine, Subtitle, ImgWrapper, Heading, Img} from './InfoElements' const InfoSection = ({ lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, darkText, description, heading, img, alt, start }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {heading} {description} ) } export default InfoSection
